- (Men screaming)
- (Horses neighing)

00:17.126 --> 00:19.837
(Horses galloping)

00:25.134 --> 00:27.845
(Swords clashing)

00:33.142 --> 00:35.436
(Men yelling)

00:40.191 --> 00:43.777
My Lady, they are upon us.

00:43.861 --> 00:47.198
The Khan has come.
Run for the desert.

